title: Let It Ride
description:
Unlucky in love every-man Dave (Seth Gamble) is shattered when he finds out that his girlfriend Wendy (Eva Lovia) cheated on him with his best friend Tommy (Michael Vegas). With help from his sexy next-door neighbor Cheryl (Ariana Marie), Dave finds his high school crush Vivian on a dating site, and Vivian guarantees Dave will get laid if he comes to visit her in Las Vegas. Now a man on a mission, Dave invites Cheryl and Tommy on a road trip to Vegas. After making a few unexpected detours and meeting several intriguing characters along the way, Dave, Cheryl and Tommy discover that when life gets complicated, itâ€™s best to just let it ride.

Cast: Ariana Marie, Ash Hollywood, Cassidy Klein, Danny Mountain, Eva Lovia, Mercedes Carrera, Michael Vegas, Richie Calhoun, Ryan McLane, Seth Gamble, Veronica Vain, Xandra Sixx
